title: New York Cosmos Meet & Greet
text:
New York Cosmos Meet & Greet Where 
3:00 p.m. Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports Meet New York Cosmos stars Danny Szetela, Jimmy Maurer, and Lucky Mkosana at Bronxville's very own Soccer and Rugby Imports on Wednesday, October 21, 2015 from 3PM-4PM. Are you the next multimillionaire? See if you have the winning ticket.
